            <p>Aatura Hospital is equipped with advanced technology and state-of-the-art facilities to support our Dermatology Department's efforts. From our fully equipped examination rooms to our on-site laboratory and surgical suites, we have the resources needed to provide comprehensive diagnostic and treatment services for all types of skin conditions.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="content3">
