            <h3>Patient-Centered Care : </h3>
            <p>At Aatura Hospital, we prioritize patient-centered care, focusing on your individual needs and concerns. Our dermatologists take the time to listen to your symptoms, answer your questions, and develop a personalized treatment plan that addresses your specific goals and preferences. We believe in empowering our patients to take an active role in their skincare journey, providing education and support every step of the way.</p>
        </div>
